**Summary:** Documents the CCPA Data Subject Access Request (DSAR) API for retrieving all user data through an asynchronous 3-step process (POST request, polling with GET, downloading files), with specific rate limits of 14.4K cost/hour, 3-day SLA, and gzipped JSON output files containing event data.

